@sigimaster14, i also had the same problem. Could not save games, and I got the "unable to save to device" error in the game. 

To fix this, go to your Bastion install location, e.g. "C:\Program Files (x86)\WB Games\Bastion".  You'll see the  folder here, e.g. "john_swarm". Right-click this folder, select properties. Go to the "Security" tab. Add "Users" in the group/users area if it isn't there already. Then give "Users" full control in the lower area, and save your changes by OK.

This worked for me!
